ected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant rrt_max performance degradation with 167.1% median increase and 77.46% p99 increase\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from normal median 36473.0 to fault median 3269.0 (median_change_ratio: 1.671, p99_change_ratio: 1.7746)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\", \n      \"reason\": \"Severe rrt_max performance degradation with 82.7% median increase and 158.27% p99 increase\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from normal median 3771.5 to fault median 3472.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.0827, p99_change_ratio: 1.5827)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory usage rate increased by 33.42% indicating potential resource pressure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate increased from 42.29% to 30.18% (median_change_ratio: 0.3342, p99_change_ratio: 0.6414)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory available bytes decreased by 23.82% suggesting memory pressure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased from 12083912704.0 to 9511884800.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.2382)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod processes metric shows potential pod lifecycle changes\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes metric detected with change patterns (median_change_ratio: 0.0, p99_change_ratio: 0.6667)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod processes metric shows potential pod lifecycle changes\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes metric detected with change patterns (median_change_ratio: 0.0, p99_change_ratio: 0.6667)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Findings:**\n\n1. **Service Performance Issues**: The most significant anomalies are in service response times, particularly `adservice-0` and `emailservice-1` showing dramatic increases in `rrt_max` (maximum response time).\n\n2. **Node Memory Pressure**: Nodes `aiops-k8s-04` and `aiops-k8s-08` show memory-related anomalies, with `aiops-k8s-04` experiencing a 33.42% increase in memory usage rate.\n\n3. **Pod Lifecycle Indicators**: Both `adservice-0` and `redis-cart-0` show `pod_processes` metric changes, suggesting potential pod restarts or process changes during the incident.\n\nThe primary issue appears to be service-level performance degradation, with `adservice-0` being the most severely affected component. The node memory pressure may be contributing to the service performance issues."}
